data.description: This is your opportunity to own a piece of Paradise in beautiful Kailua Town! Hokulani in Kailua is the ideal location for a dream beach lifestyle! This stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo comes with new laminate flooring, spacious rooms, 1 covered parking and pet friendly.  If you are seeking breathtaking beauty all around, a charming small-town feel, and vibrant local shops and restaurants, Hokulani in Kailua is your spot! This gem won't last! Contact your favorite Realtor for a showing.
